{"type": "article", "id": 55891, "title": "Burberry 换 Logo，以及，去年中国跨境进口零售电商交易额达 1.5 万亿元  | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-08-02T12:12:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 2910, "name": "Hugo Boss"}, {"id": 17704, "name": "千百度"}, {"id": 189, "name": "Burberry"}, {"id": 248, "name": "COS"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180802185544R6c9PyhEDONZ4tlH.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/business-news/financial/prada-touts-strategies-as-leathergoods-rtw-see-rebounds-1202768450/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Prada 集团上半财年净利润同比增长 10.7%</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 截至 6 月 30 日的六个月内，Prada 集团销售额同比增长 3% 至 15.3 亿欧元，净利润同比增长 10.7% 至 9540 万欧元。以固定汇率计算，营收增长 9%。Carlo Mazzi 将业绩复苏原因归结为四点策略：改善用户体验、以数字化吸引年轻客群、更新零售网络、与电商合作。</p><p>从具体品牌来看，Prada 和 Miu Miu 业绩均有所提升。Prada 销售额增长 4.1% 至 12.3 亿欧元；Miu Miu 营收增长 2% 至 2.35 亿欧元，Prada 集团主席 Carlo Mazzi 称 Miu Miu 计划在两三年内将销售额提升至 8 亿欧元以上；Church's 受批发渠道调整影响，营收下降 6.6% 至 3200 万欧元。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/business-news/financial/hugo-boss-sales-up-earnings-slip-in-q2-1202768750/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hugo Boss 第二季度销售额增长但利润下跌</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 第二季度 Hugo Boss 净销售额增长 3% 至 6.53 亿欧元，略高于分析师预期；运营利润下跌 8% 至 7400 万欧元，净利润下跌 7% 至 5400 万欧元。欧洲和中国市场的强劲销售表现以及批发渠道回暖，助推了销售额增长，但汇率浮动以及运营支出的上升对利润产生了负面影响。</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/usstock/c/2018-08-02/doc-ihhehtqf7347127.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\">2017 年中国跨境进口零售电商交易规模达 1.5 万亿元</a>&nbsp;</strong>|&nbsp;由西窗科技（北京）有限公司 8 月 2 日发布的研究报告显示，2017 年中国跨境进口零售电商交易的规模达到了 1.5 万亿元人民币，具有跨境电商购物经验的消费者在电商购物人群中的占比高达 67%。</p><p>过去一年内，中国跨境电商消费者的人均跨境电商购物次数达到 15 次。其中，高频次购买人群（过去 12 个月内跨境购物累计超过 20 次的用户）占比 26%。跨境电商消费金额超过 1 万元人民币的用户已达 53%，超过 2 万元人民币的用户已达 15%。跨境电商消费者最常购买的产品是化妆品（84%）、服饰鞋靴（82%）、电子产品（74%）和食品（64%）。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/business-news/retail/chinas-c-banner-cancels-deal-to-buy-struggling-house-of-fraser-1202768387/\" rel=\"nofollow\">千百度放弃收购英国高端百货&nbsp;House of Fraser</a>&nbsp;</strong>|&nbsp;千百度国际控股有限公司原于今年 5 月宣布将从三胞集团旗下南京新百货受众收购 House of Fraser 51% 股份，但目前已决定放弃该交易，原定的 7000 万英镑注资也将取消。消息发布后，千百度股价下跌 5.33% 至每股 0.7 港元。<br></p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Burberry-unveils-new-logo-and-monogram,1003303.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Burberry 换上了新 Logo 和新字体</strong></a>。</p><p>新 Logo 由 Peter Saville Studio 设计，灵感来自 Burberry 1908 年曾推出的一款字体。这个消息由创意总监 Riccardo Tisci 在他的个人 Instagram 账号上公布，配文：“Past | Future. Thank you #petersaville #beginning”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802194947Cvc3WKMmEjAbuyTF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/345708/shuiyuanxizipinpai-official-kiko-yongyixiliexianyifashou/\" rel=\"nofollow\">水原希子品牌 Official Kiko 推出泳衣系列</a>。</strong></p><p>泳衣系列包括四套比基尼和连体泳衣，以及两款不同颜色的衬衫式长罩衫。每套泳衣的售价均为 6980 日元（ 约 430 元人民币），购买渠道仅限<a href=\"https://officekiko.com/collections/swimwear\" rel=\"nofollow\">官网</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190218268JrwcFUatk7xNO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190058xOAVf2ygdKN1EIwi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190534PLEBfkpVod47xKrF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190147NkrXC9nTqZxlR23f.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190132hjQBtxqYyFCp35aI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190108gjJ9ynX7R6uKFmeO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190123tlioRykLITOJxY2Z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190139Hdo0O18eFsijzRtc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190232U9FWOD87pLlJNsA5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190252b4hMrNgfl1VinzRj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190303WeZsaO9jF1ciznYS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190316k6ljJfBqTSQ9yuVm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190327mbLKt24Y1fFvpWU6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190337zFZAVS241IiMXWRJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190352ZpJm6rYEny4uxGN8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190402y1Bb4L0GvRQN5YDh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190411kmsrg354QD8KSZFf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190424HaNCr9AX5uxZUnDe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190441GCw2EhPRD6ZaFWj5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190450CB2mgEI3OXPjpiaA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190506Ex6ugY1JiXRfcKzV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190524jslNBoZaLk4P9pey.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802190610PnhTafKilMRgNd8y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/345520/choubeishijianchangda-8-nianchanel-fabufinal-fittings-and-backstageyingji/\" rel=\"nofollow\">CHANEL 发布《FINAL FITTINGS AND BACKSTAGE》影集</a></strong>。</p><p>这本影集共计 768 页、1136 张照片，分为四册，包括高级时装、成衣、Cruise 和艺术大师四个部分，由 CHANEL 御用摄影师 Benoît Peverelli 过去 8 年在后台拍摄的内容集结而成，定价 85 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802191442XlzfEeT2UAdbZmW3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599692\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802191505gCTyijVnaIuKZQMp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802191459G0kZLfMDESHOXazd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018080219145282GqSrODxymdZRa5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802191525WRckqJwlUCV0XPgz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600308\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802191535vxSoehQgVPRdrUc8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/345594/huangzitaochengwei-evisu-quanxinpinpaixingxiangdaiyanren/\" rel=\"nofollow\">黄子韬成为日本潮牌 EVISU 最新品牌形象代言人</a></strong>。<br></p><p>本次大片由中国摄影师陈漫拍摄。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201808021916236rNBS1c4HFCjYfod.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600575\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802191637l8MN4CKehv5dEc3F.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599717\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802191647gzwI3l0T8DxB1rbM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600567\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802191717UutOK0SDTE3j7Nra.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.289398\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/345587/kardashian-jenner-jiazuquanshi-calvin-klein-qiudongzuixinguanggaodapian/\" rel=\"nofollow\">CALVIN KLEIN 推出秋冬最新广告大片</a></strong>。</p><p>由 Kardashian-Jenner 家族中五位话题人物&nbsp;Kim、Kourtney、Khloe、Kendall 和 Kylie 出镜。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201808021919581tIdRThcJGxw3viK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802191936Gx14MiBCmvUl7Y5z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802191925ncYloTgeP3u5M2tS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802191942L1mXNlKH08FMBcdP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802191950JOMh2fx4ckWPFESH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802192012X0YuqFo9eHikxENz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/345298/ripndip-dongjing-pop-up-store-kaicui/\" rel=\"nofollow\">以“中指猫”著称的洛杉矶品牌 RIPNDIP 8 月 3 日至 19 日在东京开了家快闪店</a></strong>。</p><p>具体地址为：THE SHARE 原宿，東京都渋谷区神宮前3-25-18 THE SHARE 原宿 1 階 104。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802192523XzHZVUewopjNsWna.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599773\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802192534VGAeY05sfvShuP8y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802192541XVe71OoYh8rIGxjB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802192549LkyPRpaBDJhAm2lS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600113\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802192559f17VMNkmUOqyc0Rn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802192607WSbokudO5a2UHifc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802192612scrxQV2koEz7ROBL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599702\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802192620sZV7hfxR3LSJiTtX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599730\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802192629zDorZxHbencMkhQS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802192636Trd25UGgPZoukMav.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802192641EPSc3sZrpjz4RlBI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600421\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802192650K31IA0tCjLRObSHw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802192655glDHAR1kWvy7VzOf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802192700Iab2KCeyt9RNhcfQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/345492/cos-fabu-2018-qiudongxiliexuanchuandapian/\" rel=\"nofollow\">COS 发布 2018 秋冬系列大片</a></strong>。</p><p>此次大片由荷兰艺术摄影师 Viviane Sassen 在位于瑞典 Österlen 的 The Kivik 艺术中心拍摄。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802192934UafBM5IXwmJtPsip.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802192944q3LpMNPX2mAo8SDl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802192954PSWUdE5yflGMvXa9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802193004GzyarcNKxq76n1IB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802193010d6FhbIofypxnw208.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599890\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802193018z9xOHUQmFZryBp1D.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599890\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802193027SJUs7XBLgtnYijk8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599890\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802193036W4Sbqrl0HoGasRUP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图为<a href=\"https://www.tylermitchell.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">&nbsp;Tyler Mitchell 摄影作品</a></p>"}